OL,3,C'Shocking and unsettling': Vegan
OL,4,Cadvert showing baby taken from mother
OL,5,Cbanned
OL,7,FAn advert for vegan charity Viva!
OL,8,Ffeaturing scenes of a human baby being
OL,9,Ftaken from its mother to protest
OL,10,Fagainst the treatment of dairy calves
OL,11,Fhas been banned for being
OL,12,Firresponsible, distressing and likely
OL,13,Fto cause widespread offence.
OL,15,FThe Advertising Standards Authority
OL,16,F(ASA) said the cinema ad, which drew
OL,17,Fon the conventions of horror films,
OL,18,Fwould have been particularly
OL,19,Fdistressing for viewers who had
OL,20,Fexperienced the loss of a child.
