OL,7,FThe ad, seen in March and April 2025,
OL,8,Ffeatured a mother placing her sleeping
OL,9,Fbaby in a cot while a lullaby played
OL,10,Fbefore a silhouetted figure suddenly
OL,11,Fappeared standing over the infant and
OL,12,Fthe room went dark.
OL,14,FThe mother switched on a light to
OL,15,Freveal a man in a suit running a
OL,16,Fbottle of milk across the bars of the
OL,17,Fcot, which was now empty, before he
OL,18,Fsaid: "You can't keep your baby
OL,19,Fbecause we want your milk."
