OL,7,FThe next scene showed a calf in a pen
OL,8,Fand a voiceover stated: "Almost every
OL,9,Fdairy calf is taken from their mother
OL,10,Fshortly after birth so most of her
OL,11,Fmilk can be sold to us. And what do
OL,12,Fyou think happens to thousands of male
OL,13,Fbabies like this one?"
OL,15,FThe words 'Dairy is Scary' and the
OL,16,FViva! logo appeared on a black screen
OL,17,Faccompanied by a loud, metallic noise
OL,18,Fand the sound of something falling to
OL,19,Fthe floor.
