OL,7,FThe ASA received 25 complaints,
OL,8,Fincluding one from The Dairy Council
OL,9,Fof Northern Ireland, that the ad was
OL,10,Firresponsible, distressing, especially
OL,11,Fto those who had lost a child, and was
OL,12,Flikely to cause serious or widespread
OL,13,Foffence.
OL,15,FViva! said they aimed to raise
OL,16,Fawareness of standard practices in the
OL,17,Fdairy industry, particularly the
OL,18,Fremoval of calves from their mothers
OL,19,Fshortly after birth.
