OL,7,FThe charity said the ad was based on
OL,8,Ffactual information and was intended
OL,9,Fto inform and encourage ethical
OL,10,Fchoices, not to shock.
OL,12,FThe ASA said viewers would understand
OL,13,Fthat the ad aimed to raise awareness
OL,14,Fof animal welfare, but said the nature
OL,15,Fof the comparison was likely to be
OL,16,Fseen as insensitive by many, and in
OL,17,Fparticular by those with experience of
OL,18,Floss or trauma around parenthood.
