OL,7,FThe ASA said: "Although the ad did not
OL,8,Fdepict the baby being harmed, and it
OL,9,Fwas not shown being physically
OL,10,Fremoved, we considered that its
OL,11,Fdisappearance was likely to be seen as
OL,12,Fshocking and unsettling.
OL,26,@oD@OOU
