OL,3,C'Shocking and unsettling': Vegan
OL,4,Cadvert showing baby taken from mother
OL,5,Cbanned
OL,7,F"We further considered that the
OL,8,Fstatement 'You can't keep your baby',
OL,9,Fin combination with the sudden
OL,10,Fdisappearance of the baby, was likely
OL,11,Fto be particularly upsetting for
OL,12,Fviewers with experience of child loss
OL,13,For fertility issues, in particular
OL,14,Fbecause the parallel with dairy
OL,15,Findustry practices was revealed only
OL,16,Fin the latter half of the ad.
OL,18,F"We considered that the message of the
OL,19,Fad did not justify the distress likely
OL,20,Fto be caused by the approach, in
OL,21,Fparticular to vulnerable audiences.
